Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.69,0:00:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got our friends close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Send everything to the pits of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail, your sun has set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dawn on Tenroujima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! The Hidden Magic didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfathomable! My magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The earth devils are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:55.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret to Master Hades's incredible \Nmagic power and longevity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:04:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a heart contained within \Nthe ship... The Devil's Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:07.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's destroyed... My magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenroujima...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's returning to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been given a new lease on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our marks are shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our magic power is returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Yes, even I... have lost to Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For those who have walked the path of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the devil will never sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's blast him with all the \Nmagic power we got back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll face my wrath for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a contract yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Goat, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capricorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, Lucy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Zoldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lucy-sama's Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capricorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this from watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Icebringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pentagram Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimoire Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,New Secret Dragon Slayer Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:30.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Exploding Lightning Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps... We showed 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We showed 'em the power of the guild \Nputting everything on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Guild!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Curses... We really have \Nzero magic power left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I am also out of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! And Gajeel-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're all safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the island returned to normal, \Nso is its divine protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off this island this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes sir, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon all the fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Where's Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She never returned to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she safe? What happened to Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:19.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did good, coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you think that's what \NI'd tell you, blockhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can set foot on Tenroujima \Nwhile you're still expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down, old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His face is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Laxus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, you're back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master sure is harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:46.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause he's a Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While he's {\i1}still{\i0} expelled, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Time to continue the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second test was interrupted \Nso it don't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just do things nice \Nand simple with a big battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with your head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat me \Nwhen you're that busted up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause right now I'm a Thunder-Fla...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of passing out is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a side effect from eating \Nsomething other than flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, shall we return to the camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to rest a bit or \Nour bodies won't hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what? I'm going to carry Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll be here to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll cheer, but you won't help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is how it shall be,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,leave this to meh, Lucy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capricorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my imagination, \Nbut is Natsu an afterthought?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you here, Mr. Cat... Are \Nyou a schoolmate of Lucy-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:59.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! I am her elder role model!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're getting along just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my father is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something very important from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I will overlook \Nwhat you did this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such weakness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me live, the next time \NI will surely crush your guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But my children beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true. My heart was destroyed, and \NTenroujima gave the youngsters power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without those coincidences, I \Nwould not have lost to your brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you fall to darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The true nature of magic is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles that are born in the darkness \Nhave come to be called "magic".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After I retired, I wished to find the truth of \Nthis world by walking deep down the path of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world, overflowing with too \Nmuch magic, is a false world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Great Magic \Nis the true magic world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that goal, I obtained all the \Nkeys I needed to resurrect Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more! I was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:06.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So close to reaching the One Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you find it, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If magic's true nature is darkness, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's light, that's fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its role changes with the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It grows, along with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every person has their own \Nversion of what "magic" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each person thinks of it differently...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can become light, or darkness... \NOr red, or even blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail lives together with freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:54.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that all from {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, will you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you sleep quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we just let him sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee, I just thought of something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Twin-tail Natsu! Isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that thing we destroyed was Hades's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was a lucky break, \Nbut we did good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we consider that as the \Npower source of the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:44.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then the Exceed Squad \Naccomplished our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are you unharmed, Lily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In far better shape than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're back, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Came back, came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I ain't really back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tryin' to tell ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman did such terrible things \Nto me while you were gone, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you punish him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? When did you two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a sec! It's kind of hard to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Lucy-sama... \NIf you'll excuse meh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch, Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will endeavor to be of \Nservice to you, Lucy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't hold back, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it would be best for you \Nto reduce your weight a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,both for health and magic power reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was carrying you earlier, \Nyou seemed a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I could begin to regulate your diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut down on all the meat and sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, maybe \Nyou could hold back a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll take care of \Nyour wounds, Levy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Wendy, why don't \Nyou rest a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:09.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I feel great now that the Tenrou \NTree is back the way it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... How did the Tenrou \NTree return to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naw, couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is so sorry! She let Zeref get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, please punish me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit Juvia as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not into that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Juvia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's Gildarts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm sure he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and got expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you old fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In one blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama! Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tellin' you, that ain't my thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy... A little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes in handy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get healed up, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You took more serious damage than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! This is when \NI can be most helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, switch places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any healing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Difference in ability doesn't \Nmatter during battle, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your heart that is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go scaring Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me straight out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I lower that fever, first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you prefer an injection?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, look what's started...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No cutting in line, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait in line, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Males!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Isn't it good to rest a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it because my breasts are too small?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tying bandages is more \Ndifficult than you'd think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tryin' to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:50.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd prefer to be punished \Nrather than punish others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is in shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just my imagination, or does the battle \Nwith Grimoire Heart already seem far in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this always happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how Fairy Tail is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what shall we do about the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's best to head back to \Nthe guild and clear our heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never could have imagined we would lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Zeref was right there before \Nus... The World of Great Magic was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones such as yourselves created me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked minds such as yours \Nsummoned Acnologia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I am announcing \Nthe end of this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world comes to an end, here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder how that blockhead's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blockhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the guy from the Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember, his name was Wally...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all coming back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:09.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? He was all edgy and funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true... But what's bringing \Nall these memories back?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.07,0:24:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Right To Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough about the past... You should worry \Nmore about whether you passed the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:23.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,10 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,10 points out of what?
